globs: **/*Test.java
alwaysApply: false
---
# Testing

- Use JUnit 5 and Mockito. No other testing frameworks.
- Write unit tests for all scoring logic and feature engineering.
- Lambda handler tests must mock all AWS SDK calls — no live AWS calls in tests.
- Test method names should clearly describe the scenario:
  `givenHighUsagePct_whenScored_thenEdgeIsPositive` style.
